message:
fix wrong usage of assertNotNull (#269)

Signature of assertNoNull() is taking "actual" as first parameter:

    public static void assertNotNull(Object actual, String message) {
        AssertNotNull.assertNotNull(actual, message);
    }

Signed-off-by: Davide Angelocola <davide.angelocola@gmail.com>

Move new PathFilter interface to the file package, annotate it with
@FunctionalInterface, and add a BasicFileAttributes parameter to accept
attributes from java.nio.file.FileVisitor.
